OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe cost of Rishi Sunak's flagship
OL,7,Fscheme has been analysed by the
OL,8,FNational Audit Office, including
OL,9,Fpayments of over #170,000 per person
OL,10,Fsent to Rwanda.
OL,12,FRishi Sunak's troubled Rwanda asylum
OL,13,Fscheme could cost half a billion
OL,14,Fpounds, plus including payments of
OL,15,Fover #170,000 per person sent to the
OL,16,Fcountry, the public spending watchdog
OL,17,Fhas found.
