OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe government has already paid Kigali
OL,7,F#220 million under the Economic
OL,8,FTransformation and Integration Fund
OL,9,Fdesigned to support Rwanda's growth,
OL,10,Fdespite flights remaining grounded due
OL,11,Fto legal setbacks.
OL,13,FIt was also already known that an
OL,14,Fextra #50 million was earmarked for
OL,15,Fthe partnership for next year. But the
OL,16,FNAO revealed the same sum will also be
OL,17,Fsent to Rwanda in 2025 and in 2026,
OL,18,Ftaking the cost to #370 million.
