OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FOn top of that, once the first 300
OL,7,Fmigrants have been relocated to
OL,8,FRwanda, ministers have agreed to put
OL,9,Fanother #120 million into the fund,
OL,10,Flifting the total to #490 million.
OL,12,FIn addition, an extra #20,000 will be
OL,13,Fpaid to Rwanda for every asylum seeker
OL,14,Frelocated there, according to the NAO
OL,15,Freport.
