OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe Home Office will also separately
OL,7,Fhand Kigali nearly #151,000 per person
OL,8,Fto cover asylum processing and
OL,9,Fintegration costs, such as
OL,10,Faccommodation, food, healthcare and
OL,11,Feducation, over five years if they
OL,12,Fstay in the country.
OL,14,FIf they decide to leave, the UK would
OL,15,Fhalt payments for that person, but
OL,16,Fwould still give Rwanda a one-off
OL,17,F#10,000 to help facilitate their
OL,18,Fdeparture.
