OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe government has already sent Kigali
OL,7,Fan advance payment of #20 million to
OL,8,Fcover these processing and operational
OL,9,Fcosts for the first arrivals.
OL,11,FShadow Home Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,12,Fslammed the plan after seeing the NAO
OL,13,Freport, calling it a "national
OL,14,Fscandal", which "the government is
OL,15,Ftrying to hide".
OL,17,F"This government have a failing Rwanda
OL,18,Fscheme that has so far sent more home
OL,19,Fsecretaries to Rwanda than asylum
OL,20,Fseekers", she said.
