OL,6,FThe Home Office has also already
OL,7,Fincurred direct costs of #20 million
OL,8,Fin establishing the agreement,
OL,9,Fincluding set-up charges for escorting
OL,10,Fmigrants on the one-way trip and
OL,11,Ftraining facilities, legal fees and
OL,12,Fstaff.
OL,14,FThis is expected to rise to #28
OL,15,Fmillion by the end of the year,
OL,16,Faccording to the watchdog.
