OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe department estimates that future
OL,7,Fcosts will include #11,000 per asylum
OL,8,Fseeker for flights to Rwanda, covering
OL,9,Fthe charter of non-commercial planes
OL,10,Fand fuel, the NAO said.
OL,12,FSome #12.6 million will also be spent
OL,13,Fon training people to escort migrants
OL,14,Fin the first year and #1 million per
OL,15,Fyear thereafter, and #1 million
OL,16,Fannually in staff costs.
