OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe NAO investigated the Rwanda plan's
OL,7,Fcosts between January and February
OL,8,Fafter the chairs of the Public
OL,9,FAccounts and Home Affairs committees
OL,10,Fraised concerns about the lack of
OL,11,Finformation available to Parliament.
OL,13,FThe initial five-year deal runs to
OL,14,FApril 2027, with payments potentially
OL,15,Fcontinuing until 2033, according to
OL,16,Fthe NAO, which did not consider its
OL,17,Fvalue for money.
