OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "It
OL,7,Fis vital we respond to illegal
OL,8,Fmigration with bold, long-term
OL,9,Fsolutions. Our Partnership with Rwanda
OL,10,Foffers just that.
OL,12,F"Doing nothing is not without
OL,13,Fsignificant costs. Unless we act, the
OL,14,Fcost of housing asylum seekers is set
OL,15,Fto reach #11 billion per year by 2026.
OL,16,FIllegal migration costs lives and
OL,17,Fperpetuates human trafficking, and it
OL,18,Fis therefore right that we fund
OL,19,Fsolutions to break this unsustainable
OL,20,Fcycle.
